{"type": "article", "id": 30609, "title": "蒲公英大头钉", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-04T22:58:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804230258QAEUT8HhMqaVOuJs.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>还记得那个经常推出可爱小物的品牌 <a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/\">OTOTO</a> 吗？旗下的办公用品也充满了让人会心一笑的有趣创意，这款由 Tania Pons 参照蒲公英设计的 Wishpins 就是其中之一。白色的“种子”其实是一根根大头针，不使用的时候将它们插回蒲公英的头部又成了一件可爱的装饰品。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.ototodesign.com/collections/all-products/products/wishpins-pushpins\">购买链接</a>，售价为 14 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160804230324aexQdhC0RTi3su4b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608042303247qla6JstY1RTbQMG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608042303241AhFLvJCagbpG60f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}